description: Welcome to 601-611 E Broadway #302, a beautifully updated penthouse offering the perfect blend of space, style, and convenience in the heart of South Boston's coveted East Side. This sunlit two-bedroom, two-bath home features an open floor plan highlighted by a large living room with a cozy gas fireplace, gleaming hardwood floors, and a renovated granite/stainless kitchen with ample storage—ideal for both relaxing and entertaining. The king-sized primary suite boasts double closets and a stone-appointed ensuite bath, while the queen-sized guest bedroom is equally spacious. Enjoy modern comforts like central air, in-unit laundry, and an off-street tandem parking space. Step outside to your expansive roof deck, shared with just one other unit owner. It offers sweeping city views—perfect for summer nights and outdoor gatherings. Located just steps from South Boston's best restaurants, bars, shops, parks, and the beach.
